"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*D9-I8WKt3S1W4pJuu01p4w.png)\\n\\n## Voting System 2.0 Goes Live\\n\\n**Update：Desktop/Mobile (All Chains)**\\n\\n\\\\*\\\\*Open the page here: \\\\*\\\\*[https://vote.wepiggy.com](https://vote.wepiggy.com/#/)\\n\\nWith the implementation of WePiggy’s multi-chain deployment plan, WePiggy has been depolyed on 4 public chains: Ethereum, OKExChain, BSC and Polygon.\\n\\nTherefore, the WPC token holder community has also expanded to multiple public chains outside the Ethereum mainnet.\\n\\nTo implement the basic principle of WePiggy community governance of “one WPC, one vote”, the core development team upgraded the original voting system and added exclusive services for calculating and storing voting power information. Now, as long as you are a WPC holder, no matter which network your WPC tokens belong to, you can use the updated voting system to vote freely.\\n\\n## Specific Rules:\\n\\n**Voting Network:** Ethereum mainnet\\n\\n**Voting Fees:** No transaction fees, just sign in the wallet\\n\\n\\\\*\\\\*Voting Group: \\\\*\\\\*WPC holders on Ethereum, OKExChain, BSC and Polygon mainnet.\\n\\n**Voting Power Calculation:**\\n\\nThe system will take snapshots of all user addresses at 0:00 every day, and calculate the total amount of WPC held by each user on all chains.\\n\\nThe voting power of each user in each formal voting is based on the snapshot taken at 0:00 (UTC+8 Time) on the voting day, one WPC one vote.\",\"timestamp\":1636596539,\"title\":\"WePiggy’s New Release: Voting System 2.0\"},\"digest\":\"09_r1Wyyx4eJ-XWktPliC2GkIKD8TAqYEpS4ck5ADU4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xf14a9FA917a5517867e4e0018f320c1F6BF6f182\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"MOToXuaua0SJZ5_SQSsecHvAOLw5KxmLTKhH_Amk1Lw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"eHu9Uej8BHwgyRn4jxCzG9EQ1R29cSjilBrFY8fm7pw\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"G8Ng_S2T8jl57xhBi5MEB